field. So I'm glad to see that. But they're going to

16:40.599 --> 16:52.435
have to work at how do you rally then the rest, the 
whole, to get behind this as a mission or a goal or

16:40.599 --> 16:52.435
objective type of thing. That would be an 
undertaking. Are there some other schools in

16:57.560 --> 17:05.530
